{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the Rhineland became free of the French occupation, my-- the-- the firm sent a case of wine to then-president Hindenburg.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we have a letter, which I can show you, thanking them for this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, they were-- they were contacted by whatever his-- Schacht, who was a high official in the Hitler regime, in 1938-- I have the letter for that too-- said he had drunk a glass of wine at one of his friends' and-- who was their customer-- and do they still have the same wine?",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He'd like to buy some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't know it was a Jewish firm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this was-- and I suppose they sold it to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But-- Tell me about your mom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was her name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "P my mother's maiden-- my mother's maiden name was Oppenheimer, O-P-P-E-N-H-E-I-M-E-R.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was Johanna and she was called Hanna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had been born in a-- a small town named Camberg, which is, oh, not very far from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's in the Taunus--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "C-A-M-B-E-R-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's in the Taunus mountains across the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her father had also been in trade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had been in-- in the grain trade in this small town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had lived in this small town for generations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a town of maybe 2,000 or 3,000 people, with a Jewish congregation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my grandmother was very active, also, in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was knitting and-- you know, with the local women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a whole group of supporters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I will tell you about my-- my other grandmother later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother's-- my mother, after she married, she didn't work, until sort of the-- the business needed some family support.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and so she helped in the business.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
